---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Water-Resistant LiDAR Camera Casing"
  description="Designed and fabricated a protective enclosure for a LiDAR camera system."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>Water-Resistant LiDAR Camera Casing</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Designed and fabricated a protective enclosure for a LiDAR camera system
      used in outdoor environments.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/images/projects/lidar-casing.jpg"
      alt="Water-Resistant LiDAR Camera Casing"
    />
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>

    <p>
      The project goal was to protect sensitive LiDAR equipment from
      environmental exposure while maintaining visibility and accessibility.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>

    <p>
      The enclosure and mounting system were designed in CAD, fabricated using
      laser-cut acrylic components, and assembled to meet environmental and
      mounting requirements.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools Used</h2>

    <p>Mechanical Design • AutoCAD • Fabrication • Prototyping</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section + section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
</style>